data.description: Stop right here for a wonderful two-bedroom, one bath ranch in Norton Shores. There is so much to offer in and around this property you do not want to miss. This well-maintained home has beautiful hardwood floors throughout, a spacious bathroom, partially finished basement and a fenced-in backyard. All this located just minutes from Lake Michigan and recreational activities abound. Come see all that this home has to offer for yourself and schedule your private showing today! NOTE: Seller will not review any/all offers until noon on Tuesday, April 16th 2024.
